===Pronunciation===
{{IPA|/ˈfiːlɪŋ/}}

===Adjective===
'''feeling'''

# [[emotionally|Emotionally]] [[sensitive]].
#: ''Despite the rough voice, the coach is surprisingly '''feeling'''.''

