===Noun===
{{en-noun|feeling|feelings}}

# [[Sense|Sensation]], particularly through the skin.
#: ''The wool on my arm produced a strange '''feeling'''.''
# [[emotion|Emotion]]; [[impression]].
#: ''The house gave me a '''feeling''' of dread.''
# (''always plural'') [[emotional|Emotional]] state or well-being.
#: ''You really hurt my '''feelings''' when you said that.''
# (''always plural'') [[emotional|Emotional]] [[attraction]] or [[desire]].
#: ''Many people still have '''feelings''' for their first love.''
# [[intuition|Intuition]].
#: ''He has no '''feeling''' for what he can say to somebody in such a fragile emotional condition.''

